<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
>> Just don't pick a human <<<P>I have a level 53 Human Magician and quite enjoyed the ride.<P>Then again, I felt significant pride when at level 51 I finally popped 200 int. Every day I feel the total benefit of being able to summon coldstones, and at level 16 when I got heatstones it was like a new game.<P>Don't knock difficulties as a bad thing. Some people will, of course, try and make things as easy as possible, but if you like a challenge take a human mage. They're actually quite playable.<P>Remember, you're not a wizard. You're sole purpose for being is not how much damage you can deal if you mana dump, you are a pet class first and foremost, a DD nuker secondly, and a utility class in a distant third.<P>I also rest easy knowing that I am without a doubt the best looking avatar in the game > <IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/eq/smile.gif">
