No offense to human mages but I would not recommend starting one if you will ever do big/epic mobs. You can get a human to 200 int but all your other resistances will suffer. I got up to 220 something and started trading out things that had more mana and resistances. When you fight dragons you will need magic, fire, cold, poison etc resistance gear and will be swapping int items most likely for them. Your int will go down fast to get that resistance up and will really suffer if you can't get it as high as possible.<P>------------------<BR>Bemidian<BR>55 Erudite Conjurer
